<div class="inner">
  <div class="page">
    <div class="lecture_questions_left_column">

      <div class="lecture_questions_outer_wrapper">

        <div class="lectures_question_title">
          A 45 year old with hyperlipidaemia who suffers from chronic stable angina not controlled with a nitrate. Which of the following is the most suitable anti-hypertensive?
        </div>

        <div class="lecture_question_blocks">

          <div class="inner_page_padding">

            <% if @answer == "true" %>
              <h1>Congratulations! That is the correct answer.</h1>
            <% else %>
              <h1>Sorry! That is not the correct answer.</h1>
              <div class="correct_lecture_answer_info" style="display: block">
                <p>The correct answer is <%= @correct_answer %></p>
              </div>
            <% end %>


            <div class="correct_lecture_answer_info" style="display: block">
              <p><%= @question.explanation %></p>

              <% if @current_question < @q_ids.length - 1 %>
                <p><%= link_to "Next Question", question_path(@next_question), :class => "red_button medium next_question_button" %></p>
              <% else %>
                <p><%= link_to "Result", questions_result_url, :class => "red_button medium" %></p>
              <% end %>
            </div>

          </div>
        </div>


      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="lecture_questions_right_column">

      <div class="questions_number_wrapper">

        <div class="questions_placement_bar">
          <div class="active_placement_bar sixty_percent"></div>
        </div>

        <p>Question <span id="current_questions_count">6</span> of 10</p>

      </div>

      <div class="questions_info_right_column_section">

        <p class="questions_info_right_column_number">28%</p>
        <p>Of users who took this test scrored on average 5/5 questions correct.</p>

      </div>

      <div class="questions_info_right_column_section">

        <p class="questions_info_right_column_number">64%</p>
        <p>Of users who took this test scrored on average 4/5 questions correct.</p>

      </div>

      <div class="questions_info_right_column_section">

        <p class="questions_info_right_column_number">2880</p>
        <p>For every video watched or correct answer you will receive 20 points to your overall score.</p>

      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>